ke":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:15:02.000Z","msg":"鐵路上蓋唔起私樓唔通起公屋比班廢柴住咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c6969a5f302ab229576b8cd6999ae1d9fbbb7d","tid":420453,"uid":80736,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:15:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇你覺得咩先叫成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果講營運同盈利呢方面又的確係幾成功</blockquote><br />\n好似完全冇人為設計喺入面，全商業活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明其實都算係公共空間嚟，又乜都唔畀做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41f687f1d278717e3fa6c20ead1eab2f686cf527","tid":420453,"uid":80736,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:16:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鐵路上蓋唔起私樓唔通起公屋比班廢柴住咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌，你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6bf25810092cfcb8e98dec760356a16067d20bc","tid":420453,"uid":26506,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:16:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>班次/轉車系統咪好<br />\n成班港奴趕返工 當然話好</blockquote><br />\n其實係轉車系統好啫</blockquote><br />\n啫香港地理好方便規劃"},{"pid":"9eca9477ed076ac4ee86a8627f696edee8de5c57","tid":420453,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:17:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇你覺得咩先叫成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果講營運同盈利呢方面又的確係幾成功</blockquote><br />\n淨係講鐵路 184% farebox recovery 個人覺得可以印喺件衫同帽度"},{"pid":"80e8df3b1715593c335bc117c755fdd88cb598d0","tid":420453,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:17:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鐵路上蓋唔起私樓唔通起公屋比班廢柴住咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n除左住呢？"},{"pid":"dfbc65cacb3c66690117fcdc71cce6eb521d9d45","tid":420453,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:18:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>班次/轉車系統咪好<br />\n成班港奴趕返工 當然話好</blockquote><br />\n都係香港地理,密度好"},{"pid":"d71a8d9aa43338db518a34d5798bc8f7a639c7f0","tid":420453,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:19:45.000Z","msg":"其實係咩全世界都同香港一樣，一入到站就只係運輸，冇仼何生活可言？"},{"pid":"583076e3e3318650599346e368eb9b404412cb49","tid":420453,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:21:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實係咩全世界都同香港一樣，一入到站就只係運輸，冇仼何生活可言？</blockquote><br />\n其實好地地一個站入面搞咁多做咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你就算講到好似日本鐵路系統咁成功都冇啦<br />\n寧願喺站外面搞仲好啦"},{"pid":"a0a583fd225afcb7621228a5ac7fb636456b6736","tid":420453,"uid":80736,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:28:48.000Z","msg":"我見韓國都有地下街，行到去下一站，香港唔可行？"},{"pid":"d5e19ece6d7603ab277fc7b2e31c496cc83ddabb","tid":420453,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:31:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你去過邊到咁多姿多彩</blockquote><br />\n睇外國歐周嗰啲，地下有好多活動，表演，香港好似全部為左傳送咁</blockquote><br />\n香港有 都唔會係文青 木結他表演<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（會係大媽廣場舞加紅歌 你睇旺角就知 一樣商業化）"},{"pid":"a57ad66663b4ea70dd98c89a4732d2e2222846b4","tid":420453,"uid":80736,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:33:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你去過邊到咁多姿多彩</blockquote><br />\n睇外國歐周嗰啲，地下有好多活動，表演，香港好似全部為左傳送咁</blockquote><br />\n香港有 都唔會係文青 木結他表演<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（會係大媽廣場舞加紅歌 你睇旺角就知 一樣商業化）</blockquote><br />\n屌，咁講，香港冇公共空間，根本係自己攞嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c35004334548c9e68cef7193cc55b4587474442","tid":420453,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T09:10:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\